    <section_number>1</section_number>
    <catch_line>Assignment Defined</catch_line>
    <order_by>1</order_by>
    <text>
        The term “assignment”, as used in this chapter, shall include every instrument purporting to transfer an interest in or an authority to collect the future wages or salary of a person.
    </text>
